-- Lockerbie Bomber al-Megrahi Is in a Coma, Close to Death, Sky News Reports
-- B y   C o l i n   K e a t i n g e
-- 2010-12-09T06:19:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-09/lockerbie-bomber-al-megrahi-is-in-a-coma-close-to-death-sky-news-reports.html
Lockerbie bomber Abdel Basset al-
Megrahi is near to death, Sky News reported, citing an
unidentified person close to his family.  The health of al-Megrahi, who is suffering from prostate
cancer, has deteriorated rapidly and he has been in a coma on
life support for around a week, the news service said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net  